 By default, this theme use the first section (folder) available in your content folder as a homepage. Create a dedicated homepage Create a _index.md in content root folder.
content ├── _index.md &lt;-- if this file exists, it is the landing page └── section-one/ &lt;-- else this section will be the home page Landing page appearance Remove navigation components from your landing page by setting options in its page frontmatter. You will be able to hide header, breadcrum, toc or footer&hellip;
 see hide options here see examples of pages rendered with theses options  Nothing but my content ! set type=&quot;raw&quot; in your home page frontmatter : only your content will be rendered, without menu, toc, headers, etc&hellip;.. example
 Use plain HTML for your homepage Remember that hugo allows you to write your content with HTML when markdown if not enough. very usefull for a landing page !
Example
--- title: Homepage type: raw --- &lt;div class=&#34;myHome&#34;&gt; Hello &lt;/div&gt;

Display one of the 2 298 icons like   
It uses :
 font-awesome 5 free icons library .more info here  This icon shortcode will display an icon in your page.
Usage    Parameter Default Description     name required name of icon (see bellow)   size none size of icon, medium, xx-small, x-small, small, large, x-large, xx-large, 11px, 2em, 20%&hellip;.   style fas use fas for solid or fab for brands see here    Tips : setting only the name as argument works too : {{&lt;icon fa-film&gt;}}` instead of `{{&lt;icon name=&quot;fa-film&quot;&gt;}}
Type a b letter after the name to use the brand version of FontAwesome {{&lt;icon fa-facebook b&gt;}}` instead of `{{&lt;icon name=&quot;fa-film&quot;&gt;}}
 Demo {{&lt; icon name=&#34;fa-save&#34; size=&#34;64px&#34; &gt;}} {{&lt; icon name=&#34;fa-save&#34; size=&#34;32px&#34; &gt;}} {{&lt; icon fa-save &gt;}}   
{{&lt; icon name=&#34;fa-github&#34; style=&#34;fab&#34; size=&#34;64px&#34; &gt;}} {{&lt; icon name=&#34;fa-github&#34; style=&#34;fab&#34; size=&#34;32px&#34; &gt;}} {{&lt; icon fa-github b &gt;}}   
icons available  https://fontawesome.com/icons?d=gallery&amp;s=brands,solid&amp;m=free/

